  <SpeechEntry>
    <EntryNumber>80</EntryNumber>
    <ID>80</ID>
    <Text>Fate is a fickle mistress. One day she might bless you with fortune, and the next, strip it all away. But you look like someone who understands. Here, take this as a token of our shared understanding.</Text>
    <Keywords>fate</Keywords>
    <Action>GIVE/CapacityIncreaseDeed/</Action>
