  <SpeechEntry>
    <EntryNumber>90</EntryNumber>
    <ID>90</ID>
    <Text>Darkness isn't just the absence of light. It's the weight one feels when hope seems lost. But sometimes, in the deepest darkness, a glimmer of hope can shine the brightest.</Text>
    <Keywords>darkness</Keywords>
    <DependsOn>-1</DependsOn>
    <Pause>1</Pause>
