    <SpeechHue>-1</SpeechHue>
  </SpeechEntry>
  <SpeechEntry>
    <EntryNumber>100</EntryNumber>
    <ID>100</ID>
    <Text>The embrace of sorrow can be chilling. But like a blanket, it also wraps around you, becoming a familiar companion. Do you seek solace in music too?</Text>
    <Keywords>embrace</Keywords>
    <DependsOn>-1</DependsOn>
