  <SpeechEntry>
    <EntryNumber>110</EntryNumber>
    <ID>110</ID>
    <Text>Ah, fortune. It can be as fleeting as a sunset or as enduring as the mountains. But its true value is in how we use it. Do you believe in fate's hand guiding your path?</Text>
    <Keywords>path</Keywords>
    <DependsOn>-1</DependsOn>
