  <SpeechEntry>
    <EntryNumber>120</EntryNumber>
    <ID>120</ID>
    <Text>Hope is the light that guides us through the darkest tunnels. Even I, in my most somber moments, cling to it. Have you found hope in unexpected places?</Text>
